Package: GuttmanHeatmap
Type: Package
Title: Annotated Heatmaps for RNA-seq Gene Expression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joel Correa da Rosa <correadarosaj@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Joel Correa da Rosa <correadarosaj@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to create richly annotated heatmaps for RNA-seq
    gene expression data. Supports significance annotations, log2 fold change
    overlays, clinical metadata, and multi-contrast comparisons using the
    ComplexHeatmap framework.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ComplexHeatmap,
    circlize,
    stringr,
    weights,
    plyr,
    tidyverse
